    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1936-05-17T11:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1936-05-17T11:00:00-05:00" n="185"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d185">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">824.00/752: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in Bolivia</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Muccio</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">La Paz</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1936-05-17T12:00:00-04:00"
                            >May 17, 1936—noon</date>.<lb/>[Received 4:40 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>21. My telegram of May 16, 7 p.m.<note n="6" xml:id="d185fn6">Not printed.</note>
                    President resigned 2 a.m. Manifesto issued by Acting Chief General Staff<note
                        n="7" xml:id="d185fn7">Lt. Col. German Busch.</note> this morning states
                    army assumes supreme mandate not to possess itself of the political power but to
                    restore order. Army to associate itself with the more popular political parties
                    to select a mixed junta. Manifesto states provisional government will respect
                    and faithfully comply with all treaties and accept international pacts.</p>
                <p>Meeting of army, Socialists and Republican Socialists leaders now in progress in
                    Government Palace awaiting instructions from Colonel Toro still in Villa
                    Montes.</p>
                <p>La Paz exceptionally quiet with soldiers patrolling streets. No information is at
                    hand from outlying centers.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Muccio</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
